    "description": "Sunteck Realty, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Property Consultant for our Patna operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Sunteck Realty:\nSunteck Realty is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Referral bonus program\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sunteck Realty!",
